products.title: Pomegranate Noir Cologne
products.description: Daring sensuality, encapsulated in scent. Ruby-rich juices of exotic pomegranate, sparked with pink pepper and Casablanca lily. Warmed by temptingly-smoky guaiacwood and patchouli.

products.title: English Pear & Freesia Lace Design Cologne
products.description: The essence of autumn. The sensuous freshness of just-ripe pears is wrapped in a bouquet of white freesias, and mellowed by amber, patchouli and woods. Luscious and golden. Etched with a decorative lace design.

products.title: Moonlit Camomile Cologne
products.description: An evening wander filled with possibility. The enchanting freshness of feathery English camomile leaves mingle with blue moonflowers, glimpsed in the garden after dark. Enveloped in the gentle sensuality of cocooning white musk.

products.title: Lime Basil & Mandarin Home Candle
products.description: Float away on a cool tropical breeze. Peppery basil and aromatic white thyme bring an unexpected twist to the scent of limes.Crafted in the English countryside in a signature glass design. Burn time approx. 45 hours. Lid included. Wax height 4.78cm, width 7.5cm.

products.title: Peony & Blush Suede Body & Hand Lotion
products.description: Peonies in voluptuous bloom, exquisitely fragile. Flirtatious with the juicy bite of red apple and the opulence of jasmine, rose and gillyflower. Mingling with the sensuality of soft, blush suede. Enriched with coconut oil, our Body & Hand Lotion is readily absorbed to instantly hydrate and condition, while its fragrance-diffusing properties help to radiate scent from the skin.

products.title: Vitamin E Body Treatment Scrub
products.description: Luxuriously revitalising, Vitamin E Body Treatment Scrub sloughs away dry surface skin cells to help retexturise and remove environmental pollutants from the skin. Non-abrasive sugar particles gently exfoliate to reveal radiant-looking skin and a more youthful glow.

products.title: English Pear & Freesia Exfoliating Shower Gel
products.description: Smoothes away impurities to help leave skin soft, smooth, and ready to moisturise. Gentle exfoliating ingredients include natural origin jojoba, castor seed oils and bamboo stem.

products.title: Vitamin E Gel
products.description: A luxurious gel that moisturises dry, dehydrated or weathered skin. Contains Vitamin E and is rich in antioxidants, which helps fortify the skin against the damaging effects of the environment.

products.title: English Mint & Ginger Lip Care
products.description: Nourishing English Mint & Ginger Lip Care. Softens, soothes and repairs dryness. Enriched with moringa butter, rose flower wax and kukui seed oil to help condition and protect lips. Scented with enlivening notes of mint. Balanced by the lively brightness of ginger. An irresistible combination of the fresh and the spicy. Perfectly-sized to take with you.

products.title: English Pear & Freesia Room Spray
products.description: Mellow the mood with the autumnal scent of a ripening orchard. Orchards of ripe pears and cool, white freesias. 175ml room spray.

products.title: Lime Basil & Mandarin Car Diffuser Set
products.description: Start the car with the zesty fragrance of Lime Basil & Mandarin. Created for use in our Car Diffuser, this Refill offers continuous scent in a smart and stylish design to enhance your journey.Take the scented route with our signature fragrance. Awaken your senses with the scent of limes, peppery basil and aromatic white thyme. Tantalising and addictive, it enlivens every drive.

products.title: Blackberry & Bay Body & Hand Lotion
products.description: Childhood memories of blackberry picking. A burst of deep, tart blackberry juice, blending with the freshness of just-gathered bay and brambly woods. Vibrant and verdant. Enriched with coconut oil, our Body & Hand Lotion is readily absorbed to instantly hydrate and condition, while its fragrance-diffusing properties help to radiate scent from the skin.

products.title: Sea Daffodil Cologne
products.description: A chance discovery along the coast: rare and exquisite white sea daffodils in the salt-blown sands of southern Italy. This solar floral, luminous and radiant with ylang ylang, is rooted in the warmth of vanilla entwined with creamy sandalwood.

products.title: Lavender & Moonflower Diffuser
products.description: Embrace the evening with a soft, serene scent. Aromatic English lavender nestles among a cocooning note of white musk and night-blooming moonflowers. Includes 10 rattan reeds to release scent continuously. For optimum effect use all 10 simultaneously.

products.title: Pomegranate Noir Scent Surround™ Diffuser
products.description: Daring sensuality, encapsulated in scent. Ruby-rich juices of exotic pomegranate, sparked with pink pepper and laced with Casablanca lily. Warmed by temptingly-smoky guaiacwood and patchouli. Dark and enigmatic. Understated and sleekly designed, our Diffusers effortlessly and continuously add an enveloping scent to any space.

products.title: Myrrh & Tonka Home Candle
products.description: Enrich the atmosphere with a captivating warmth. The golden sap of the Namibian myrrh tree harvested in the desert mingles with warm vanilla notes of the tonka bean. Crafted in the English countryside in a black glass design. Burn time approx. 45 hours. Wax height 4.78cm, width 5cm.

products.title: Myrrh & Tonka Shower Oil
products.description: Our cleansing Shower Oil, with nourishing sunflower and castor seed oils, helps to gently smooth and soften skin. Leaving it deliciously scented with Myrrh & Tonka. The rich, hand-harvested sap of the Namibian myrrh tree, mingling with the warm almond and lush vanilla notes of the tonka bean. The conditioning formula creates a rich lather, perfect for skin that needs a little extra care. A luxurious addition to your daily routine.
